<seg id=1> China Becomes Big Eiderdown Producer and Exporter </seg>
</hl>
<p>
<seg id=2> XINHUA NEWS AGENCY WIRE Beijing, Sept. 1 (Zhou Liang reporting):  China's eiderdown industry has risen abruptly over the last ten years, and has now become an important light industry in the country. Annual export amounts and values account for one half of world trade in eiderdown, receiving wide praise in the international market. </seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg id=3> The eiderdown industry began developing quickly in the mid-1980s in China, taking advantage of excellent resources and labor power, as well as laying stress on importing advanced foreign technology and equipment. Production amounts and quality improved considerably. </seg>
<seg id=4> According to partial statistics, China currently has more than three thousand companies working in the industry producing eiderdown and processing products from eiderdown. Among them, larger-scale companies number more than six hundred. Employees in the industry number about three hundred thousand. Annual production capability is more than 50 million pieces, valued at eight billion yuan. </seg>
<seg id=5> Over ten years of an open market have allowed China to become the world's main producer and exporter of eiderdown. Annual exports are near thirty thousand tons, products number more than twenty million pieces, and foreign exchange earnings have reached 820 million U.S. dollars. Clothing exports account for more than 50 percent of the industry's total exports. </seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg id=6> According to reports, the quality of China's eiderdown products is steadily improving. </seg>
<seg id=7> The government singled out fifty-six producers of eiderdown clothing products for an assessment of the first half of this year. The products of forty-seven of them passed inspection, accounting for 84 percent of the total. </seg>
<seg id=8> In the competitive market, the following brands stand out as being well-known: Yaha of Jiangxi, Yililan of Beijing, Gelanshi of Guangdong, and Tiange of Sichuan. </seg>
</p>
